Package library.persistence.implementation

Class DatabaseService

java.lang.Object
library.persistence.implementation.DatabaseService
All Implemented Interfaces:
Service
public class DatabaseService extends Object implements Service
DatabaseService implements the interface Service. It retrieves data from the Database and returns them either in Lists of the database types or directly in objects of the database types.
